lass=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/5/4/thumb_286922644.jpeg\" /></div><div class=\"photo\"><img src=\"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/6/e/5/thumb_280458149.jpeg\" /></div>          </div>          <p style=\"line-height:16px\">(English is below) Th t ngy 17/04, chng ta s gp g trong bui Saigon WordPress meetup vi cc ch  sau: 1&#xfe0f;&#x20e3; Vi s tr li ca anh Jamie Madden, l Lead developer ca plugin WC Vendors (https://www.wcvendors.com/). Anh s chia s v  ti: WooCommerce v cc cng thanh ton online  Vit Nam Cc bn c th tm hiu thm v Jamie qua link s&#8230;</p>     </div>     <p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;\"><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/Saigon-WordPress/events/260335342/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"mu_button\"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p></div>\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ch  1: WooCommerce v cc cng thanh ton ti Vit Nam</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch  c chia s bi Jamie, l tc gi ca plugin WC Vendors v cng l Co-organizer ca meetup. Trong ch  ny, Jamie  chia s v gii p thc mc lin quan n vic s dng cc cng thanh ton ti th trng Vit Nam, nhng im mnh, yu ca tng cng thanh ton.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3565-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-784\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3565-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3565-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3565-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3565-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Jamie ang chia s v WooCommerce v cc cng thanh ton ti Vit Nam</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ch  2: WooCommerce v Google Shopping</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch d c chia s bi anh Mi Hunh. Ch  ca anh lin quan n vic bn hng trn Google Shopping v cch tch hp gia 2 nn tng WooCommerce v Google Shopping.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3572-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-785\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3572-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3572-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3572-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3572-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><figcaption>Anh Mi Hunh ang chia s v Google Shopping v WooCommerce</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>a im</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Officience Vietnam : 16A L Hng Phong, Phng 12, Qun 10</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-684\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254.png 1098w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-300x211.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-768x539.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-1024x719.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1098px) 100vw, 1098px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tm speaker</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Mt trong nhng kh khn ca ti mnh  l tm kim ngi  chia s cho meetup, v c ngi chia s th mi c th t chc meetup c. V vy mong cc bn cng ng gp bng cch ng k ch  m bn mun ni  phn comment, hoc gi email v a ch: nguyenvanduocit@gmail.com</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Ti tr</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Xin cm n ti:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong><a href=\"https://officience.com/en?utm_source=wordpress_saigon&amp;ref=worddpress_saigon\">Officience Vietnam</a></strong>  lun ng hnh v h tr a im cho meetup.</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://weglot.com/?utm_source=wordpress_saigon&amp;ref=worddpress_saigon\">Weglot</a></strong>  h tr kinh ph cho thc n.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<h3>Mt vi hnh nh lin quan</h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3577-1024x1024.jpg\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/04/IMG_3577-10