arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ri lon v gic ng: y l triu chng rt hay gp v khin ngi bnh rt kh chu bi n din ra dai dng v kh cha, au u. a phn cc trng hp thng mt ng, kh ng, ng khng su gic, mt s th ri lon thi gian ng, ngy ng m thc, au u sau khi ng dy</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tuy nhin, cc triu chng thiu nng tun hon no kh nhn bit v rt d nhm ln vi chng au na u nguy him Migraine nhng thng b quy chp l mc phi chng thiu nng tun hon no do tnh ph bin ca n. V vy chng ti cung cp mt s thng tin v bnh au na u Migraine:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">au na u Mifrgraine l bnh l au u do cn nguyn mch, gy ra bi s co gin bt thng ca mch mu no do thay i t ngt nng  cht dn truyn thn kinh Serotonin  nhng ngi c nng  nn Serotonin thp. Triu chng in hnh l au na u kiu git nhi theo nhp mch p, c th lan sang c u. Trong cn au, bnh nhn c th s nh sng, ting ng v au tng ln khi vn ng.   bnh nhn Migraine c du hiu tin triu nh m mt, nhn thy vt sng ngon ngoo nn d nhm ln vi triu chng thiu nng tun hon no. iu tr au na u Migraine cn kin tr lu di v y l chng bnh mn tnh. Ti cc nc pht trin, tho dc Feverfew c s dng ph bin nht gip iu ha nng  Serotonin trong no, nh  kim sot au na u hiu qu.</span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Nguyn nhn v bin chng</strong></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cc bnh mn tnh c cho l mt trong nhng nguyn nhn hng u gy ra bnh thiu nng tun hon no. Ch yu l x va hoc x cng mch mu lm hp lng mch mu khin lng mu ln no b gim, thoi ha t sng c chn p cc mch mu dn ln no, bnh tng huyt p, bnh mu nhim m, ng, cc bnh v tim mch nh van tim, ri lon nhp tim, suy thn</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Mt s yu t khc cng khin nguy c mc bnh cao nh bnh l bo ph, t vn ng, gp nhiu p lc, stress, nghin bia, ru, thuc l</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Do cc biu hin ca bnh thiu mu no kh ph bin v d gp c  nhng ngi bnh thng nn bnh nhn thng d ch quan v l l vic iu tr. Nu  bnh tin din lu ngy c th s dn n nhng bin chng nguy him, c bit l tai bin mch mu no  nguy c t vong cao. Theo thng k th s lng ngi t vong do tai bin mch mu no cao th 3, ch ng sau cc bnh v tim mch v ung th.</span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>iu tr v phng bnh</strong></span></li>\n</ol>\n<p></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bnh thiu nng tun hon no tuy nguy him nhng khng phi l khng c cch phng nga v iu tr hiu qu. Chng ta nn trang b nhng kin thc v cn bnh ny v c k hoch phng bnh tht sm.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khi b bnh, cn tm hiu nguyn nhn  iu tr bnh tn gc, kt hp vi iu tr triu chng. Hin nay c rt nhiu thuc iu tr triu chng ca thiu mu no nh au u, chng mt, mt ng ty vo c ch bnh sinh m thuc hiu qu vi bnh nhn ny nhng li t hiu qu vi bnh nhn khc. V vy,  iu tr bnh hiu qu v an ton nht, bn phi i khm trc tip v c k n ti cc c s y t chuyn khoa.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bn cnh vic dng thuc, bnh nhn cng phi kt hp vi vic sinh hot, n ung hp l v th dc thng xuyn; trnh xa cc thc phm c hi hay cht kch thch nh thuc l, bia, ru, kim sot ng mu, hn ch ti a cc yu t gy stress.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Vi bnh nhn b thiu mu no mn tnh, p dng nhiu cch cha tr khng hiu qu, th Hot Huyt An Thn Tanaka PlusVi chnh l la chn u vit, l gii php ton din cho bnh nhn thiu mu no, thc y mnh m tun hon mu ti no v t chi, tng sc bn mch mu no, ng gim cc triu chng au nhc u, chng mt, bun nn cho ngi bnh mt cch t nhin.</span></p>\n<!-- /wp:tadv/classic-paragraph -->", "6 IU CN GHI NH V BNH THIU NNG TUN HON NO", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "223-revision-v1", "", "", "2019-05-20 13:34:03", "2019-05-20 13:34:03", "", "223", "http://mualatang.com/2019/05/20/223-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
